  nodes:
  - portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 595a385a1a0d2574e97151f20417b396, type: 3}
    text: 'Here''s a quick rundown of the controls: On your turn use WASD or Arrow
      keys to move your character around within their movement range. Movement range
      is the light blue highlighting and attack range is the light green. (Space to
      continue)'
  - portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4daf07e256f630f42848b5bde5396bb0, type: 3}
    text: The line represents the path that they took this turn; try not to move through
      an enemy's vision cone.
  - portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 595a385a1a0d2574e97151f20417b396, type: 3}
    text: Take an action or end your turn by pressing Space or Enter. If you control
      multiple characters you can also use tab to switch between them.
  - portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 961b23b8958548d48859712ec53d38df, type: 3}
    text: Press C during your turn to survey the map and inspect the stats of the
      various combatants.
  - portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 595a385a1a0d2574e97151f20417b396, type: 3}
    text: Red walls block line of sight and movement, yellow walls only block movement.
  - portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 595a385a1a0d2574e97151f20417b396, type: 3}
    text: 'Now for your mission: defeat all the enemies (purple squares) to beat the
      level.'
